{
  "stem": "11771.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They're putting the, the, the cotton what's growing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it became cotton from the straw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's usually-- that's the purpose of this kind of building.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I came in, into the buildings.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was also a, a little man-made canal with water, for fish probably.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I got in in this building.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I start to feel a little warmer, because I start to shaking from cold to hot, [INAUDIBLE] wet.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I dry off myself, laid over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in the-- and I fall asleep over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I lost my sense of directions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I lost my sense of conscious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I didn't know where I am.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I was looking instinctively for shelter, and to some-- to dress myself on me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I, I, I slept a while.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then I saw stack with hay.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You know, the farmers, they are cutting the grasses in this kind of peat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they're concentrating it in big stacks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "When it's winter, it's freezing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "When it's snow, they're coming in, and they're taking the hay into the barracks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But summertime, it's impossible to do it, so they are cutting it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I saw this stack of hay just before daylight comes on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I dig in myself in such a stack of hay.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was close, about 100 meter off from this place where I was-- from this building.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "When I dig in into this stack of hay, and it was-- the hay was dry and it was like, like needles to my body.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But I adjust myself to them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They was sticking me, to my-- my body was so painful.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But I find myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
